---

<section class="bg-gray-100 py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight sm:text-5xl">Our Clients Love To Talk About Us</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Hear from our satisfied clients about how we've transformed their spaces with creativity, precision, and care.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-full mx-auto relative">
    <div class="flex overflow-x-auto scroll-smooth snap-x snap-mandatory pb-4 hide-scrollbar">
      <button
        class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 -ml-4 w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center z-10 hidden md:flex"
      >
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          ><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg
        >
      </button>

      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full lg:w-1/2 px-4 snap-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-6">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Client feedback</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              transformed our space into something truly special. Their design ideas were creative, and the execution was flawless. We couldn't be
              happier with the result! transformed our space into something truly special. Their design ideas were creative, and the execution was
              flawless. We couldn't be happier with the result!
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-2">
              <img src="/path-to-avatar-john-doe.jpg" alt="John Doe Avatar" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">John Doe</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Managing Director, Spherule</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="md:w-1/2 rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
            <img src="/path-to-space-image.jpg" alt="Transformed Space" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full lg:w-1/2 px-4 snap-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-6">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Another Happy Client</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Our living room feels so much more open and inviting now. The team was incredibly professional and delivered exactly what we envisioned,
              on time and within budget. Highly recommend their services!
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-2">
              <img src="/path-to-avatar-jane-smith.jpg" alt="Jane Smith Avatar" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Jane Smith</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Homeowner</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path d="M12 .587l3.692 7.568L24 9.77l-6 5.856L19.423 24 12 20.272 4.577 24 6 15.626 0 9.77l8.308-1.615L12 .587z"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
            <img src="/path-to-space-image2.jpg" alt="Another Transformed Space" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button
        class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 -mr-4 w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full shadow-md flex items-center justify-center z-10 hidden md:flex"
      >
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          ><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
        >
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center mt-6 gap-2">
      <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-gray-800 rounded-full"></span>
      <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-gray-300 rounded-full"></span>
      <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-gray-300 rounded-full"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Ocultar la barra de desplazamiento pero permitir el scroll */
  .hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }
  .hide-scrollbar {
    -ms-overflow-style: none; /* IE and Edge */
    scrollbar-width: none; /* Firefox */
  }
</style>
